# Occultist Killing

Currently removed until Rework

As the Occultist, you can curse players or kill them.
Cursing a player works the same as spelling as a Spellcaster.

  • Switch Action via:
    • Kill
    • Vent
    • Double Click
  • Curses look like spells
    • ON: Curses will have the same icon as spells
    • OFF: Curse will have a different icon
